            <summary class="faq__q">What’s the safest “fast money” loop for absolute beginners?</summary>
            <div class="faq__a">Courier-style jobs are the safest start: low risk, low gear loss, and they teach navigation. Once you can finish loops reliably, move into bounties or FPS for faster scaling.</div>
          </details>

