            <summary class="faq__q">How do I avoid losing gear and wasting money?</summary>
            <div class="faq__a">Don’t over-buy. Carry only what you’ll use, keep backup basics in storage, and avoid high-risk FPS missions until you can complete the safe loop consistently.</div>
          </details>

          <details class="faq__item">
            <summary class="faq__q">What should I upgrade first with my first earnings?</summary>
            <div class="faq__a">Quality-of-life first: upgrades that reduce downtime (faster travel, survivability basics) usually beat “cool” purchases. Buy small, verify you still enjoy the loop, then scale up.</div>
          </details>

